high_descs: Turn around and move forward, then turn right to find the sink.
Open the bottom left cabinet and take out the ladle.
Carry the ladle and turn around then turn left to locate the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the ladle inside, on a plate.
Pick up the plate from inside the fridge, and shut the door.
Carry the plate and turn to the left, then left again. Face the sink on the right side.
Place the plate and ladle on the counter, to the left of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Move a plate from the fridge and place it on the counter with a ladle.

high_descs: Turn around and veer right to the sink.
Take out the ladle in the bottom left cabinet under the sink.
Turn around and walk left to the fridge.
Place the ladle on the plate in the fridge.
Pick up the plate.
Turn around and veer right back the sink.
Place the plate on the counter to the left of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a plate with a ladle on it on a counter.

high_descs: Turn around and move to the sink on the right.
Open the cupboard below the sink and take out the ladle.
Turn around and move to the fridge on the left.
Place the ladle on the plate inside the fridge.
Pick up the plate with the ladle.
Turn to the left and move to the sink on the right.
Place the plate with the ladle on the counter to the left of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Organize the plate and ladle to prepare to be washed.
